            br
            p.
              A classy website, custom emails, domain and hosting setup&mdash;whatever you need, we can do it.
              With Leung Enterprises, getting an awesome new website for your business is simple and straightforward.
            br
            a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg(href='./about') More About Us
    .jumbotron.full-page.light-bg#work
      .container-fluid
        .row.wow.fadeIn
          .col-sm-6
            a(href='./portfolio/saffron-indian')
              img.img-responsive.box-shadow(src="/img/saffron.jpg")
          .col-sm-5.col-sm-offset-1
            h2 The Art of Blending Spices
            br
            p.
              Saffron Indian Kitchen is a fine dining establishment with locations in Ambler and Bala Cynwyd, PA.
              Leung Enterprises was commissioned to create a high-quality website which would showcase the restaurant's
              selection of Indian cuisine, highlighting items such as samosas and tikka masala.
            br
            a.btn.btn-info.btn-lg.hidden-xs(href='./portfolio/saffron-indian') More Info
        br
        br
        br
        .row.text-center.hidden-xs
          .col-sm-4.wow.fadeIn(data-wow-delay='0.3s')
            a.portfolio-link(href='./portfolio/ashe-attire')
              #ase
                .overlay
                  div
                    p.no-margin-bottom Ash&eacute; Attire
                    span.help-block Spreading diversity through clothing
          .col-sm-4.wow.fadeIn(data-wow-delay='0.5s')
            a.portfolio-link(href='./portfolio/neoscreen')
              #neo
                .overlay
                  div
                    p.no-margin-bottom NeoScreen Products
                    span.help-block Innovative screen repair toolkit
          .col-sm-4.wow.fadeIn(data-wow-delay='0.7s')
            a.portfolio-link(href='./portfolio/wissahickon-track')
              #track
                .overlay
                  div
                    p.no-margin-bottom Wissahickon Track and Field
                    span.help-block Faster than fast
          .clearfix
          br
          br
        .row.text-center
          .col-xs-12.text-center
            a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg(href='./portfolio') Our Portfolio
    .jumbotron.half-page.transparent-bg.parallax-window.text-center.trianglify#services(data-parallax='scroll' data-speed='0.25' data-image-src='/img/milkyway.jpg')
      .container
        h1.text-light Our Services
        p Need something special?  Drop us a line and we can work something out.
        br
        br
        .row
          .col-sm-4.wow.fadeIn
            i.ion-code-working.text-12x
            h2.text-light Custom Website Design
            p.
              We offer premium website design services, both with custom-code and Wordpress.  Our designs
              are fully responsive and work on both mobile and desktop.
          .col-sm-4.wow.fadeIn(data-wow-delay='0.3s')
            i.ion-ios-search.text-12x
            h2.text-light Search Engines (SEO)
            p.
              We'll boost your business's ranking on search engines, helping you to increase your sales and revenue.
          .col-sm-4.wow.fadeIn(data-wow-delay='0.5s')
            i.ion-folder.text-12x
            h2.text-light Domain and Hosting
            p We offer full domain setup and hosting maintenance for a small monthly fee.
          .clearfix
          br
          br
          a.btn.btn-transparent.btn-lg(href='./services') Our Services
    include partials/footer

block scripts
  script.
    var video = document.getElementById('video-bg');
    video.playbackRate = 0.333;
  script(src='/js/trianglify-0.3.1.min.js')
  script.
    function genTriangles() {
      var height = window.innerHeight;
      var width = window.innerWidth;
      var colorFunc = function(x, y) {
        return 'hsl(0,0%,'+Math.floor(Math.abs(x*y*100))+'%)';
      };
      var pattern = Trianglify({
        // in case the jumbotron is a bit bigger
        height: height * 2,
        width: width,
        cell_size: 100,
        color_function: colorFunc
      });
      var image = pattern.png();
      var elements = [".trianglify"];
      var afterElements = elements.map(function(el) {
        return el + '::after';
      });
      var css = "<style>" +
                  elements.toString() + " { " +
                    "position: relative;" +
                  "}" +
                  afterElements.toString() + " {" +
                    "content: '';" +
                    "display: block;" +
                    "z-index: -1;" +
                    "position: absolute;" +
                    "top: 0;" +
                    "bottom: 0;" +
                    "left: 0;" +
                    "right: 0;" +
                    "opacity: 0.4;" +
                    "background: url(" + image + ");" +
                  "}" +
                "</style>";
      $('head').append(css);
    }
    genTriangles();
    $(window).resize(function() {
      genTriangles();
    });
    
